Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.54,0:00:08.30,style.default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Like a cruel angel{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.55,0:00:14.77,style.default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Become a legend, young boy{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.40,0:00:30.95,style.default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}When a blue wind{\c}{\i0}\N{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Knocks on the door to your heart{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.16,0:00:38.16,style.default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}You just gaze back at me{\c}{\i0}\N{\i1\c&Hffffff&}And smile oh so gently{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.12,0:00:45.88,style.default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}So eager for something{\c}{\i0}\N{\i1\c&Hffffff&}You touch so softly{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.13,0:00:52.76,style.default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Those innocent eyes{\c}{\i0}\N{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Know nothing of the fate that awaits{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.68,0:00:59.77,style.default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}But one day, you will realize{\c}{\i0}\N{\i1\c&Hffffff&}That upon your back{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.19,0:01:07.69,style.default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}You have wings{\c}{\i0}\N{\i1\c&Hffffff&}You can fly to the faraway future{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.78,0:01:12.24,style.default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}The cruel angel's thesis{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.45,0:01:15.62,style.default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}One day, you'll take off through a window{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.16,0:01:19.71,style.default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}If your overflowing pathos{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.91,0:01:23.13,style.default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Leads you to betray your memories{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.63,0:01:26.80,style.default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Then embrace the heavens and shine bright{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.30,0:01:30.88,style.default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Become legend, young boy{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.35,0:01:39.52,style.default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Good morning, Shinji. How are you feeling?{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.02,0:01:42.94,style.default,,0,0,0,,I'm used to it. It's not so bad now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.15,0:01:44.23,style.default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Glad to hear it.{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.52,0:01:49.36,style.default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Eva egress points, emergency{\c}{\i0}\N{\i1\c&Hffffff&}ordnance structures, recovery points...{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.48,0:01:51.99,style.default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}-Do you have them all memorized?{\c}{\i0}\N-I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.07,0:01:53.66,style.default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Let's go over it one more time, then.{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.03,0:01:57.58,style.default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}An Eva usually runs off an external,{\c}{\i0}\N{\i1\c&Hffffff&}cabled power feed.{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.29,0:02:00.62,style.default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}When it switches to internal battery{\c}{\i0}\N{\i1\c&Hffffff&}in an emergency,{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.70,0:02:03.21,style.default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}capacity limitations mean{\c}{\i0}\N{\i1\c&Hffffff&}it can only run at full for one minute.{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.42,0:02:06.42,style.default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}It can run for five minutes at most{\c}{\i0}\N{\i1\c&Hffffff&}by using a low gain mode.{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.88,0:02:10.84,style.default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}That's as far as our science can go.{\c}{\i0}\N{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Understood?{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.17,0:02:12.17,style.default,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.26,0:02:15.30,style.default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Then we'll pick up from yesterday.{\c}{\i0}\N{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Starting induction mode.{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.64,0:02:23.60,style.default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Center the target... and pull the trigger.{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.73,0:02:29.86,style.default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Keep calm. Center the target.{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.19,0:02:31.19,style.default,,0,0,0,,Pull the trigger...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.20,0:02:37.20,style.default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Next!{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.100,0:02:49.29,style.default,,0,0,0,,I'm amazed that Shinji was willing\Nto go through with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.59,0:02:54.01,style.default,,0,0,0,,He does whatever he's told.\NThat's how he makes his life easier.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.68,0:03:01.35,style.default,,0,0,0,,Center the target, pull the trigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.83,0:03:22.58,style.default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}And now we go to Matsuzaki,{\c}{\i0}\N{\i1\c&Hffffff&}where Natsuko Shinohara is waiting!{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.20,0:03:26.37,style.default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Hello! Good morning! Shinohara here!{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.83,0:03:31.09,style.default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}This morning, we're here to do{\c}{\i0}\N{\i1\c&Hffffff&}some diving at Matsuzaki in West Izu!{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.75,0:03:34.55,style.default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Misato? It's morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.30,0:03:38.72,style.default,,0,0,0,,I just got off duty...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.05,0:03:44.02,style.default,,0,0,0,,I just need to show up\Nbefore sunset today, so let me sleep...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.47,0:03:45.81,style.default,,0,0,0,,Well, I need to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.73,0:03:47.94,style.default,,0,0,0,,Right, today's Thursday!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.65,0:03:50.81,style.default,,0,0,0,,Take out the burnable garbage, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.94,0:03:52.77,style.default,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.78,0:03:56.45,style.default,,0,0,0,,Have you gotten settled in at school?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.07,0:03:58.07,style.default,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.41,0:04:00.53,style.default,,0,0,0,,Okay... Have a nice day.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.20,0:04:02.20,style.default,,0,0,0,,I'm off, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.47,0:04:19.22,style.default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.14,0:04:21.97,style.default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's you, Ritsuko.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.26,0:04:24.81,style.default,,0,0,0,,So, are things working out\Nwith the new boyfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.89,0:04:28.14,style.default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Boyfriend? Oh, you mean Shinji.{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.44,0:04:30.94,style.default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}It's been two weeks since{\c}{\i0}\N{\i1\c&Hffffff&}he started school, and nothing.{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.19,0:04:33.44,style.default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Nobody ever calls him.{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.82,0:04:34.65,style.default,,0,0,0,,Calls him?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.32,0:04:39.15,style.default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}It's a necessity, so I got him{\c}{\i0}\N{\i1\c&Hffffff&}a cell phone a while ago.{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.57,0:04:43.70,style.default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}But there's no sign of him ever using it{\c}{\i0}\N{\i1\c&Hffffff&}or anyone ever calling him.{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.04,0:04:48.41,style.default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}I'm starting to think{\c}{\i0}\N{\i1\c&Hffffff&}he doesn't have any friends.{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.71,0:04:53.54,style.default,,0,0,0,,Shinji might be the sort of person\Nwho can't make friends easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.25,0:04:56.80,style.default,,0,0,0,,Have you ever heard of\Nthe Hedgehog's Dilemma?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.13,0:04:59.72,style.default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Hedgehog? Those spiky animals?{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.01,0:05:03.80,style.default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Hedgehogs have a hard time sharing{\c}{\i0}\N{\i1\c&Hffffff&}warmth with other hedgehogs.{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.89,0:05:07.85,style.default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}The closer they get, the more{\c}{\i0}\N{\i1\c&Hffffff&}they hurt each other with their quills.{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.43,0:05:10.23,style.default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}People are also like that.{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.73,0:05:13.27,style.default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}I think some part of Shinji{\c}{\i0}\N{\i1\c&Hffffff&}is afraid to take that risk{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.36,0:05:16.23,style.default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}because he's afraid of being hurt.{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.61,0:05:18.49,style.default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}He'll figure it out eventually.{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.57,0:05:23.11,style.default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Part of growing up is trying again{\c}{\i0}\N{\i1\c&Hffffff&}and again and using trial and error{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.53,0:05:27.99,style.default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}to work out the right distance{\c}{\i0}\N{\i1\c&Hffffff&}to avoid hurting each other.{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.30,0:05:42.47,style.default,,0,0,0,,What is it, Class Rep?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.05,0:05:45.47,style.default,,0,0,0,,Did you deliver all those\Nstudy guides like I asked?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.72,0:05:47.60,style.default,,0,0,0,,Oh, um... Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.60,0:05:51.48,style.default,,0,0,0,,Actually, it doesn't seem like\Nanyone's home at Tohji's place.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.73,0:05:54.40,style.default,,0,0,0,,You and Suzuhara are friends,\Naren't you, Aida?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.77,0:05:56.98,style.default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you worried that he's\Nmissed school for two weeks?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.65,0:05:59.40,style.default,,0,0,0,,Maybe he got hurt badly or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.07,0:06:03.66,style.default,,0,0,0,,In that incident with the giant robot?\NBut the TV said no one got hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.74,0:06:06.91,style.default,,0,0,0,,No way. You saw the crater\Nat Mt. Takanosu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.70,0:06:09.87,style.default,,0,0,0,,Units were called up from\Nnot only Iruma and Komatsu,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.95,0:06:12.50,style.default,,0,0,0,,but even from Misawa and Kyushu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.83,0:06:17.38,style.default,,0,0,0,,There must have been way more than ten\Nor 20 casualties. Some fatalities, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.21,0:06:21.21,style.default,,0,0,0,,-Tohji!\N-Suzuhara!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.88,0:06:25.59,style.default,,0,0,0,,Well, damn.\NThere sure are a lot fewer of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.89,0:06:28.97,style.default,,0,0,0,,They evacuated. They all transferred out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.60,0:06:32.60,style.default,,0,0,0,,That's what happens when there's\Na huge battle in the middle of your city.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.85,0:06:37.27,style.default,,0,0,0,,I bet you're the only guy that loves this.\NGetting to see a firefight up close.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.36,0:06:38.36,style.default,,0,0,0,,I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.57,0:06:41.40,style.default,,0,0,0,,So, what's up, Tohji? Why did you\Nstay home from school for so long?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.82,0:06:44.65,style.default,,0,0,0,,Did you get mixed up in that mess?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.53,0:06:46.70,style.default,,0,0,0,,My kid sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.66,0:06:51.87,style.default,,0,0,0,,My kid sister got buried\Nunder a pile of rubble.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.33,0:06:55.54,style.default,,0,0,0,,She survived, but she's been\Nin the hospital ever since.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.08,0:06:59.46,style.default,,0,0,0,,My old man and uncle\Nwork at the labs, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.92,0:07:02.30,style.default,,0,0,0,,They can't tear themselves away\Nfrom work right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.67,0:07:05.88,style.default,,0,0,0,,So if I don't stay with her,\Nshe'd be all alone in the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.64,0:07:10.22,style.default,,0,0,0,,I swear, the pilot of that damn robot\Nis totally worthless!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.31,0:07:12.02,style.default,,0,0,0,,He pisses me off so bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.39,0:07:14.94,style.default,,0,0,0,,He's supposed to be on our side,\Nand he trashed the city!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.14,0:07:18.52,style.default,,0,0,0,,About that. Have you heard the rumors\Nabout the new transfer student?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.90,0:07:20.07,style.default,,0,0,0,,Transfer student?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.48,0:07:21.90,style.default,,0,0,0,,That kid over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.11,0:07:26.53,style.default,,0,0,0,,He transferred in while you were gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.07,0:07:30.03,style.default,,0,0,0,,He showed up right after the battle.\NDon't you think that's fishy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.50,0:07:34.50,style.default,,0,0,0,,All rise!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.37,0:07:42.42,style.default,,0,0,0,,And so, this is how humanity\Nwas faced with its greatest ordeal.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.71,0:07:44.84,style.default,,0,0,0,,In the closing year of the 20th Century,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.92,0:07:49.68,style.default,,0,0,0,,a meteor of extraordinarily high mass\Nmade impact on Antarctica.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.76,0:07:53.56,style.default,,0,0,0,,That continent of ice\Nwas melted in an instant.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.93,0:07:57.02,style.default,,0,0,0,,Sea levels rose,\Nthe planet's axis shifted,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.19,0:08:02.40,style.default,,0,0,0,,and abnormal weather assaulted the globe,\Nthreatening all life on Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.77,0:08:07.11,style.default,,0,0,0,,Half of mankind,\Nalong with thousands of species,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.20,0:08:09.41,style.default,,0,0,0,,were forever lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.49,0:08:13.41,style.default,,0,0,0,,This is what we now refer to\Nas the Second Impact.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.74,0:08:16.79,style.default,,0,0,0,,Economic collapse,\Nethnic conflicts, and civil wars.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.04,0:08:19.96,style.default,,0,0,0,,Those who survived\Nexperienced hell on earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.21,0:08:23.92,style.default,,0,0,0,,ARE YOU REALLY THE PILOT OF THAT ROBOT?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.00,0:08:28.55,style.default,,0,0,0,,In fifteen short years, we have\Nbounced back and rebuilt so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.13,0:08:30.97,style.default,,0,0,0,,While this is surely...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.05,0:08:32.85,style.default,,0,0,0,,IT'S TRUE, ISN'T IT?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.93,0:08:35.18,style.default,,0,0,0,,...a testament to\Nthe greatness of mankind,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.27,0:08:40.98,style.default,,0,0,0,,it is also the result of the blood,\Nsweat, tears, and hard work
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.06,0:08:42.98,style.default,,0,0,0,,of your fathers and mothers.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.65,0:08:49.49,style.default,,0,0,0,,I was living in Nebukawa at the time.\NBut that's now underwater...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.11,0:08:52.57,style.default,,0,0,0,,Come on! Class isn't over yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.66,0:08:53.87,style.default,,0,0,0,,Sit down!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.95,0:08:56.12,style.default,,0,0,0,,There you go,\Nbossing everyone around again!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.20,0:08:57.83,style.default,,0,0,0,,-Give it a rest!\N-I will not!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.41,0:09:00.100,style.default,,0,0,0,,-Wow!\N-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.08,0:09:04.63,style.default,,0,0,0,,-So, how were you chosen?!\N-Was there a test or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.79,0:09:07.55,style.default,,0,0,0,,-Weren't you scared?\N-What's the cockpit like?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.76,0:09:10.22,style.default,,0,0,0,,Um, well... All that stuff is secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.93,0:09:14.76,style.default,,0,0,0,,-Aw, don't hold out on us!\N-What's the name of that robot?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.85,0:09:18.39,style.default,,0,0,0,,I don't know for sure, but everyone\Ncalls mine "Eva" or "Unit 01."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.98,0:09:20.10,style.default,,0,0,0,,Any special attacks?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.19,0:09:22.94,style.default,,0,0,0,,They said it has something called a...\Na "something" Knife...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.02,0:09:26.40,style.default,,0,0,0,,It uses vibration to...\NNo, ultrasound or something...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.48,0:09:29.44,style.default,,0,0,0,,This is so cool!\NYou're the pride of our school!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.86,0:09:30.90,style.default,,0,0,0,,That's so awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.40,0:09:33.20,style.default,,0,0,0,,And that brings us to--
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.83,0:09:37.70,style.default,,0,0,0,,-That's all for today.\N-Where do you live, Ikari?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.79,0:09:39.58,style.default,,0,0,0,,All rise! Bow!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.08,0:09:44.71,style.default,,0,0,0,,Hey, at least try to be polite\Nat the end of class, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.76,0:09:58.31,style.default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, newbie. But I have to punch you.\NI couldn't live with myself otherwise.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.31,0:10:05.98,style.default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, buddy.\NHis little sister got hurt in that battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.40,0:10:08.11,style.default,,0,0,0,,That's just how he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.07,0:10:13.07,style.default,,0,0,0,,It's not like I pilot that thing\Nbecause I want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.64,0:10:46.77,style.default,,0,0,0,,Emergency call-up. I'll meet you there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.78,0:10:59.20,style.default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}A special state of emergency has{\c}{\i0}\N{\i1\c&Hffffff&}been declared for the Toukai region{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.28,0:11:01.91,style.default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}and the surrounding mid-Kanto area.{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.25,0:11:05.33,style.default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}All residents, proceed to your{\c}{\i0}\N{\i1\c&Hffffff&}designated shelter immediately.{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.100,0:11:07.75,style.default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}I repeat...{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.52,0:11:25.39,style.default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Visual confirmation of target.{\c}{\i0}\N{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Has entered territorial waters.{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.73,0:11:27.81,style.default,,0,0,0,,All personnel to\Ncondition one battle stations.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.23,0:11:30.69,style.default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Roger! Prepare for{\c}{\i0}\N{\i1\c&Hffffff&}surface-to-air intercept!{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.98,0:11:33.99,style.default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Initiating deployment of Tokyo-3{\c}{\i0}\N{\i1\c&Hffffff&}into combat configuration.{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.07,0:11:36.11,style.default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Retracting central block structures.{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.14,0:12:10.10,style.default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Retraction of central block structures,{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.19,0:12:12.36,style.default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}as well as Wards 1 through 7,{\c}{\i0}\N{\i1\c&Hffffff&}now complete.{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.44,0:12:15.03,style.default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Government and appropriate agencies{\c}{\i0}\N{\i1\c&Hffffff&}have been notified.{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.11,0:12:19.99,style.default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Air defense systems currently{\c}{\i0}\N{\i1\c&Hffffff&}operating at 48% capacity.{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.53,0:12:22.62,style.default,,0,0,0,,Status of noncombatants and civilians?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.83,0:12:25.41,style.default,,0,0,0,,Evacuation has been reported as completed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.50,0:12:27.46,style.default,,0,0,0,,TOKYO-3 DISASTER PREVENTION DIV.\NAREA: 2000m2, MAX OCCUPANCY: 250
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.54,0:12:29.62,style.default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Students in grades 1-9,{\c}{\i0}\N{\i1\c&Hffffff&}stay with your class.{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.71,0:12:32.84,style.default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Residents, remain with other{\c}{\i0}\N{\i1\c&Hffffff&}residents of your block.{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.84,0:12:34.84,style.default,,0,0,0,,Damn, again?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.38,0:12:37.17,style.default,,0,0,0,,Nothing but text again, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.80,0:12:41.97,style.default,,0,0,0,,It's a press blackout.\NThey're keeping us civilians in the dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.47,0:12:44.39,style.default,,0,0,0,,Damn it,\Nthis is a once-in-a-lifetime deal!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.56,0:12:51.27,style.default,,0,0,0,,The 4th Angel strikes\Nwhile Commander Ikari is away.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.85,0:12:53.19,style.default,,0,0,0,,It's sooner than we thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.77,0:12:58.19,style.default,,0,0,0,,Last time was after a 15-year gap.\NThis time, only three weeks went by.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.28,0:13:00.45,style.default,,0,0,0,,Not very considerate of others, are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.78,0:13:02.53,style.default,,0,0,0,,Women hate people like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.91,0:13:11.54,style.default,,0,0,0,,What a waste of taxpayer money.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.33,0:13:15.46,style.default,,0,0,0,,The Council is requesting\Nthat we launch an Evangelion again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.13,0:13:17.21,style.default,,0,0,0,,Bunch of pushy jerks.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.92,0:13:19.59,style.default,,0,0,0,,We were going to do that anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.43,0:13:25.93,style.default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Entry sequence has started.{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.76,0:13:29.52,style.default,,0,0,0,,-{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Ionizing LCL.{\c}{\i0}\N{\i1\c&Hffffff&}-Pressure clamps unlocked.{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.19,0:13:34.40,style.default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Father isn't here to watch,{\c}{\i0}\N{\i1\c&Hffffff&}so why am I doing this again?{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.90,0:13:38.53,style.default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}I was even beaten up because of it...{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.74,0:13:45.74,style.default,,0,0,0,,Hey, I need to talk to you\Nabout something.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.03,0:13:47.04,style.default,,0,0,0,,Shoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.12,0:13:48.29,style.default,,0,0,0,,In private.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.83,0:13:49.87,style.default,,0,0,0,,All right, all right...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.25,0:13:53.25,style.default,,0,0,0,,-Hey, Class Rep.\N-Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.62,0:13:55.54,style.default,,0,0,0,,We need to take a leak!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.04,0:13:58.46,style.default,,0,0,0,,Oh, come on! You should have\Ndone that before we came here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.30,0:14:00.80,style.default,,0,0,0,,Okay, what's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.01,0:14:03.63,style.default,,0,0,0,,I have to see one before I die, just once.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.80,0:14:05.14,style.default,,0,0,0,,What? That fight up top?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.22,0:14:08.64,style.default,,0,0,0,,There's no way to know when or if\Nthe enemy will come again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.72,0:14:10.98,style.default,,0,0,0,,Kensuke, you're a real piece of work.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.06,0:14:13.60,style.default,,0,0,0,,Sir! This might be\Nour only opportunity, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.69,0:14:16.52,style.default,,0,0,0,,So, please, help me unlock the door!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.61,0:14:19.98,style.default,,0,0,0,,-Going outside might get you killed!\N-The same thing might happen in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.19,0:14:22.45,style.default,,0,0,0,,If I might die either way,\NI want to see what's going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.53,0:14:25.53,style.default,,0,0,0,,You dumbass. Nerv's there to stop that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.74,0:14:28.24,style.default,,0,0,0,,Exactly, and what is Nerv's\Ndecisive battle weapon?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.53,0:14:30.58,style.default,,0,0,0,,It's the new kid's robot!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.95,0:14:35.17,style.default,,0,0,0,,He protected us in the last battle.\NAnd then you had to deck him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.25,0:14:36.46,style.default,,0,0,0,,Twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.38,0:14:41.01,style.default,,0,0,0,,We'll all be dead\Nif he doesn't get in and pilot it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.67,0:14:45.68,style.default,,0,0,0,,Tohji, isn't it your duty\Nto watch him fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.09,0:14:47.68,style.default,,0,0,0,,Fine, fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.18,0:14:52.18,style.default,,0,0,0,,You're a real slave to\Nyour passions, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.81,0:14:57.06,style.default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Shinji, are you ready for launch?{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.40,0:14:58.23,style.default,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.31,0:15:02.86,style.default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Remember. Pallet rifle volley fire as{\c}{\i0}\N{\i1\c&Hffffff&}you neutralize the enemy's A.T. Field.{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.28,0:15:05.15,style.default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Just like we practiced. Can you handle it?{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.24,0:15:06.07,style.default,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.45,0:15:07.28,style.default,,0,0,0,,Launch!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.30,0:15:30.64,style.default,,0,0,0,,Wow, it was worth all the trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.97,0:15:31.97,style.default,,0,0,0,,And here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.48,0:15:41.32,style.default,,0,0,0,,There he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.74,0:15:46.74,style.default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}-A.T. Field raised.{\c}{\i0}\N-Center the target...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.95,0:15:49.53,style.default,,0,0,0,,-{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Proceed according to plan. Okay, Shinji?{\c}{\i0}\N-Pull the trigger...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.62,0:15:50.62,style.default,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.100,0:15:59.21,style.default,,0,0,0,,That idiot! That smoke and dust\Nis obscuring the target!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.01,0:16:12.14,style.default,,0,0,0,,What the hell?\NHe's getting his ass kicked already!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.22,0:16:13.06,style.default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.39,0:16:14.77,style.default,,0,0,0,,We're putting out a spare rifle!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.52,0:16:16.35,style.default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Grab it!{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.89,0:16:20.02,style.default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Shinji? Shinji!{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.86,0:16:22.19,style.default,,0,0,0,,Oh, man...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.73,0:16:25.03,style.default,,0,0,0,,That beatdown\Nmust have really rattled him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.11,0:16:26.11,style.default,,0,0,0,,Screw you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.13,0:16:49.47,style.default,,0,0,0,,Umbilical cable severed!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.72,0:16:52.68,style.default,,0,0,0,,Eva has switched to internal power!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.22,0:16:55.85,style.default,,0,0,0,,Active time remaining,\Nfour minutes, 53 seconds!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.19,0:17:05.23,style.default,,0,0,0,,It's headed right for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.40,0:17:12.87,style.default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Shinji, are you okay? Shinji?!{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.20,0:17:15.33,style.default,,0,0,0,,-{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Damage report!{\c}{\i0}\N-{\i1\c&Hffffff&}None. He's good to go.{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.46,0:17:29.09,style.default,,0,0,0,,-Shinji's classmates?!\N-What are they doing there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.94,0:17:43.52,style.default,,0,0,0,,Why isn't he fighting back?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.85,0:17:47.36,style.default,,0,0,0,,Is it because we're here?\NHis hands are tied!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.03,0:17:51.53,style.default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Unit 01 active time remaining,{\c}{\i0}\N{\i1\c&Hffffff&}three minutes, 28 seconds!{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.03,0:17:56.45,style.default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Shinji, let those two into your cockpit!{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.58,0:18:01.75,style.default,,0,0,0,,After you've retrieved them, retreat!\NWe'll start over!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.96,0:18:05.42,style.default,,0,0,0,,Do you think you can allow unauthorized\Ncivilians into that entry plug?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.38,0:18:07.46,style.default,,0,0,0,,I'm authorizing them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.88,0:18:09.96,style.default,,0,0,0,,You're overstepping your authority,\NCapt. Katsuragi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.88,0:18:14.59,style.default,,0,0,0,,Unit 01 active time remaining,\Nthree minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.84,0:18:19.06,style.default,,0,0,0,,Mission on hold under standing orders.\NEject the entry plug in the meantime.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.23,0:18:24.40,style.default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}You two, get in! Hurry!{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.90,0:18:27.52,style.default,,0,0,0,,What is this, water?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.02,0:18:29.57,style.default,,0,0,0,,My camera! My camera!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.53,0:18:35.16,style.default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Abnormalities in nerve circuits!{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.62,0:18:37.87,style.default,,0,0,0,,There are two foreign bodies\Nin the entry plug.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.28,0:18:40.29,style.default,,0,0,0,,There's noise mixed in\Nwith the nerve pulses.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.50,0:18:48.75,style.default,,0,0,0,,Now! Retreat!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.97,0:18:57.43,style.default,,0,0,0,,-{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Use recovery route 34. Pull back to...{\c}{\i0}\N-Hey, newbie! She said to retreat!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.51,0:18:59.64,style.default,,0,0,0,,-Don't run away. Don't run away.\N-Newbie!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.47,0:19:01.35,style.default,,0,0,0,,Don't run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.35,0:19:03.81,style.default,,0,0,0,,Progressive Knife equipped!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.77,0:19:10.57,style.default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Shinji, obey my order! I said to retreat!{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.07,0:19:12.07,style.default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Shinji!{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.11,0:19:17.95,style.default,,0,0,0,,That idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.84,0:19:39.80,style.default,,0,0,0,,Unit 01 active time remaining, 30 seconds!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.30,0:19:41.14,style.default,,0,0,0,,Twenty-eight!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.51,0:19:43.64,style.default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Twenty-seven! Twenty-six!{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.93,0:19:44.93,style.default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Twenty-five!{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.61,0:19:51.15,style.default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Fourteen! Thirteen!{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.69,0:19:53.15,style.default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Twelve! Eleven!{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.44,0:19:54.86,style.default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Ten! Nine!{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.36,0:19:56.65,style.default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Eight! Seven!{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.20,0:19:58.61,style.default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Six! Five!{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.91,0:20:00.41,style.default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Four! Three!{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.70,0:20:02.12,style.default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Two! One!{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.00,0:20:11.92,style.default,,0,0,0,,Eva-01 has ceased operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.09,0:20:14.21,style.default,,0,0,0,,Target is completely inactive.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.67,0:20:59.84,style.default,,0,0,0,,It's been three days now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.59,0:21:03.35,style.default,,0,0,0,,Since they read us the riot act?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.80,0:21:06.81,style.default,,0,0,0,,Since he stopped coming to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.97,0:21:07.98,style.default,,0,0,0,,Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.43,0:21:10.39,style.default,,0,0,0,,The transfer student, who else?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.35,0:21:14.23,style.default,,0,0,0,,-I wonder what he's up to.\N-You worried about him?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.27,0:21:17.32,style.default,,0,0,0,,Who said I was worried?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.40,0:21:20.53,style.default,,0,0,0,,It's because you're so bull-headed\Nin spite of being so socially awkward.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.20,0:21:24.03,style.default,,0,0,0,,If you had apologized\Nthe last time we saw him,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.20,0:21:26.70,style.default,,0,0,0,,you wouldn't have spent\Nthree whole days agonizing over it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.12,0:21:29.41,style.default,,0,0,0,,Here. This is the new kid's phone number.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.50,0:21:32.33,style.default,,0,0,0,,If you're worried, call him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.03,0:22:02.07,style.default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}TO BE CONTINUED
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.43,0:23:11.43,style.default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Unable to get a handle on his feelings,{\c}{\i0}\N{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Shinji runs away from even Misato.{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.77,0:23:14.77,style.default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}However, the organization{\c}{\i0}\N{\i1\c&Hffffff&}unceremoniously drags him back.{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.85,0:23:16.81,style.default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}No one there had any kind words for him.{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.02,0:23:19.52,style.default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Next episode! "Rain, After Running Away"!{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.86,0:23:21.90,style.default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Tune in next time{\c}{\i0}\N{\i1\c&Hffffff&}for lots more fan service!{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.40,0:23:25.65,style.default,,0,0,0,,Translator: Dan Kanemitsu\NSubtitle Editor: David Fleming
